originalText.text: Without a doubt the best jewelry store in the West Village or anywhere ! Precious and semi-precious stones in unique designs. Fabulous and attentive owner/designers. My sister gave me a pair of earrings a few years ago and I have been a devotee ever since. Each NYC visit includes a visit to this fabulous store.

originalText.text: Innaya is a West Village gem! My husband and I were visiting from out of town and stumbled upon her boutique where her beautiful artistry and jewelry lured me inside where I fell in love with a few of her rings and other pieces! Their beauty is dwarfed only by how warm and welcoming Inna is.  My husband surprised me months later with the ring I had been told had sold when I later inquired, after returning homeâ€” and it made the experience all the better. I love that Inna was in on the surprise and that I have this beautiful piece to remember her and our experience in the shop that resonates the same warmth we felt that cold February day in NY.  Thank you!

originalText.text: Christmas 2021 marks the third or fourth time I've purchased items from this beautiful little shop in the West Village and I couldn't be more pleased with the experience. The jewelry is absolutely gorgeous and unique, all designed and handcrafted by the owners and made with ultra high quality precious metals and stones. The prices, in my opinion, are exceptionally reasonable and fair considering the craftsmanship involved and the chic location of the shop.  If you are looking for a piece that is special or extraordinary you simply must pop in here and at least look at what they have - no doubt you'll walk out an impressed new customer just like me!
